* {{tl|DNBfirst}}—Can be placed on the same line as {{Tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}}} to allow readers who do not have access to ODNB to see older versions of the text now in the public domain. This is particularly useful if there is a version of the text available on Wikisource. Please refrain from using this template if the same DNB article is already available in the Wikipedia article via {{Tl|Cite DNB}} or {{Tl|DNB}}.
* {{tl|Who's Who}}
* [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Dictionary of National Biography]].
* {{tl|Subscription or libraries}}—A template for use when a subscription may be required or the source may be at a library.

